name: H&H Fly Fishing 101 Package.
description: H&H Fly Fishing 101 Package We've traveled the dark depths of the Internet in search of a complete kit that allows the beginner to hit the river right out of the box. Unfortunately we couldn't find anything that offered reliability, quality and affordability. So in true DIY fashion we created our own! Here at H&H we truly believe in community and we wanted to bring some of our up and coming industry colleagues in to help us round out these kits. We chose two American companies who pride themselves on innovation and quality. Dryft Waders and SmithFly Bags are a perfect fit and a great way to enter the sport in affordable quality and style. We've tried to think of everything we had to piece together when we were getting started. Running from shop to shop or garage sale to garage sale can be a pain so if you like the one stop shop, this is the kit for you! The 101 kit includes the following... H&H mesh back hat and Fly Corps tee shirt, H&H DIY Fly Tying Kit, sticker and drink koozie Scientific Anglersâ„¢ 4-piece Fly Combo features everything you need to get started on the path to fly fishing for trout. This fishing kit includes all the basics - a 4-piece rod, reel, 5/6 weight, line, leader and tippet, all spooled up on a Concept 2 quality disk reel. Also included are appropriate flies and an instructional DVD. SmithFly 1X wading pouch. (Part of the SmithFly interchangeable bag system) These bags are seriously cool and the interchangeable system allows for you to create the combination that works best for you and your needs. SmithFly makes durable American made bags to hold all your gear. Dryft Fishing S13 Adrenaline Waders. Dryft breathable waders offer style and affordability. A one year warranty and a proven track record of performance make this a great wader choice for the beginner and the pro. Allen felt sole wading boots. Affordable quality wading boots to get you on the water and keep you on your toes. ***PLEASE ENTER SHIRT AND BOOT SIZE IN THE "NOTE TO SELLER" SECTION OF THE PAYPAL CHECK OUT SYSTEM. ***REMEMBER WHEN CHOOSING YOUR BOOT SIZE. CHOOSE AT LEAST ONE SIZE LARGER BOOT THAN YOU WOULD WEAR REGULARLY. THAT WAY YOU CAN WEAR THICK WOOL SOCKS AND STILL HAVE ROOM TO MOVE. ***CURRENTLY ONLY AVAILABLE IN THE LOWER 48 UNITED STATES. ***PLEASE ALLOW TWO WEEKS FOR DELIVERY.
